title: Or Maybe Yesterday
description:
Molitor is a Canadian Indie/Rock artist from Niagara Falls, Ontario.

Or Maybe Yesterday is the debut release from the 19-year old solo artist. The EP was recorded, mixed, mastered and released independently from his college dorm room in Toronto, Ontario.

Follow him on Twitter here: @MolitorOfficial

1) Remember Me

2) Star Bright

3) While Falling

4) For Those Eyes

5) Bathroom Mirror

6) To The Moon
